Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:49.54,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　痛みでさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:51.34,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:02:03.68,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}傷を負った　世界を知った
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:08.69,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}強く儚い果実
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:15.61,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}つきまとう　責任の重たさで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:20.11,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}熟れ落ちて　土へと還る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:23.03,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　痛みでさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:25.79,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　通じ合えば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:30.00,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}この血の滾りを解放してけ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:31.00,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}そこにいますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:35.92,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}衝突に戦々恐々　降り立つ堕天使
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:41.18,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}早々に早熟な実も　食らい尽くすの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:46.89,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}もがく度に　蒼穹に聴いた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:50.10,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}君を確かめた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:50.93,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}あっけない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.93,0:02:54.73,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}無い無い　馴れ合い　有り余った慟哭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:03:00.07,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}葛藤に混乱していく　今を生きて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:06.95,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(960,3)}それでもまだ　僕らは目指した
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:08.50,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\fs45\pos(960,54)}Follow me Follow you　痛みでさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:11.12,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　通じ合えば
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:13.84,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　何処まででも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.84,0:03:15.29,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}Follow me Follow you
